divs: Sighting DetailsI was out at my mother-in-law's acreage Saturday evening, with my husband and brother-in-law. We were watching a demolished shed being burned. I like to star gaze, and have been doing so for some time now. Around 10:15 pm (right after it dark), I happen to look up and seen this star-like object traveling from the Southwest at an alarming speed. I pointed it out to my husband and brother-in-law and we watched as it traveled out of sight to the Northeast.
